m-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; bac=
kground-color: #ccc;">announced that it is planning a=C2=A0stock split</a>,=
 missing April Fool=E2=80=99s Day by hours. The stock opened up almost 14% =
on Friday, though it lost those gains and closed down on the day. We <a hre=
f=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/27253239.266604/aHR0cHM6=
Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDMtMjkvc3RvY2stc3B=
